<p>Move it or lose it: Her rumored partner Alan Bersten arrived a little after, chatting with Johnny Weir and fellow dancer Britt Stewart before heading in </p>

<p>Her rumored partner Alan Bersten arrived a little after, chatting with Johnny Weir and fellow dancer Britt Stewart before heading in.</p>

<p>He showed off his arms wearing a button down tank that he teamed with khaki bottoms, a red backpack and retro-looking NASA fanny pack up front.</p>

<p>Navarro Cheer coach Monica Aldama didn't waste one minute getting into the studio, seen charging in wearing dark exercise duds with Bulldog red shoes and a matching bag.</p>

