<p>As always, Johnny Weir was ready for the spotlight, striking an elegant pose in the parking lot.</p>

<p>His snug, black leggings and tank were understated but the former Olympian couldn't help but add some pizzazz with florescent green shoes that perfectly complemented his Kelly green Birkin bag. </p>

<p>The Pennsylvania native topped his look off with a Philadelphia Eagles hat and a Louis Vuitton duffel for good measure.</p>

<p>Maybe-partner Britt Stewart smiled behind her mask as she watched Johnny do his thing.</p>

